# Third-Party Software Licenses

This document is generated by [`cargo-about`](https://github.com/EmbarkStudios/cargo-about) from the dependencies in `Cargo.lock`. It enumerates every third-party Rust crate that is statically linked into the released `kiln-server` and desktop binaries, along with each crate's license text.

The kiln source code itself is licensed under the [MIT License](LICENSE). Each dependency below is governed by its own license, reproduced verbatim in the per-license sections at the end of this file.

To regenerate this document after a dependency change:

```sh
cargo install cargo-about --version 0.6.6 --locked
cargo about generate --workspace --all-features -o THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md about.hbs
```

